  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join us on Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the Thrill of RC Revolution!</h2>Welcome to the exhilarating world of radio-controlled car racing, where unforgettable moments of intense immersion await you! The game seamlessly combines strategy, skill, and speed to offer an experience that stands as a timeless classic in the realm of competitive racing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Mayhem and Cooperative Gameplay</h2>Dive into the heart-pounding multiplayer mayhem with a wide array of competitive and cooperative modes. Race against your friends or team up with them to share victory on a split screen. Each race presents an opportunity to push your limits and climb the ranks in our rewarding progression system!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/6ecbbbd314196945a8dd40dad9667fb7.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/6ecbbbd314196945a8dd40dad9667fb7.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of Cars, Tracks, and Customization Options</h2>Choose from a diverse collection of cars and tracks, each with its own unique challenges and characteristics! Customize your car to suit your racing style and witness firsthand how it affects your performance on the track.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to Pick Up, Difficult to Master</h2>Our game strikes the perfect balance between accessibility and challenge! With realistic and aesthetic physics, a variety of gameplay options, and a relentless focus on fun, we cater to both casual gamers and seasoned veterans. Enjoy exhilarating drifts, power slides, overtaking maneuvers, crashes, and collisions as you hone your skills on the track!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/205ab708ad874a9462ff08717ab8793b.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/205ab708ad874a9462ff08717ab8793b.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayability with a Creative Track Builder</h2>The fun doesn’t stop at just racing! Unleash your creativity with our intuitive and customizable track builder. Design your own tracks, complete with clever obstacles and hazards. Set up your own championship events using our championship editor, adding to the replayability and competitive spirit of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the Thrill of RC Revolution!</h2>Welcome to the exhilarating world of radio-controlled car racing, where unforgettable moments of intense immersion await you! The game seamlessly combines strategy, skill, and speed to offer an experience that stands as a timeless classic in the realm of competitive racing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/74c204eda98cfcc9cd81879ab97806ac.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Mayhem and Cooperative Gameplay</h2>Dive into the heart-pounding multiplayer mayhem with a wide array of competitive and cooperative modes. Race against your friends or team up with them to share victory on a split screen. Each race presents an opportunity to push your limits and climb the ranks in our rewarding progression system!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/6ecbbbd314196945a8dd40dad9667fb7.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/6ecbbbd314196945a8dd40dad9667fb7.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Variety of Cars, Tracks, and Customization Options</h2>Choose from a diverse collection of cars and tracks, each with its own unique challenges and characteristics! Customize your car to suit your racing style and witness firsthand how it affects your performance on the track.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/64de018ae699f51af366d6f774196811.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to Pick Up, Difficult to Master</h2>Our game strikes the perfect balance between accessibility and challenge! With realistic and aesthetic physics, a variety of gameplay options, and a relentless focus on fun, we cater to both casual gamers and seasoned veterans. Enjoy exhilarating drifts, power slides, overtaking maneuvers, crashes, and collisions as you hone your skills on the track!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/205ab708ad874a9462ff08717ab8793b.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/205ab708ad874a9462ff08717ab8793b.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Replayability with a Creative Track Builder</h2>The fun doesn’t stop at just racing! Unleash your creativity with our intuitive and customizable track builder. Design your own tracks, complete with clever obstacles and hazards. Set up your own championship events using our championship editor, adding to the replayability and competitive spirit of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.poster.avif?t=1710631464\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.webm?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347040/extras/089abd5300176866fc2d1a6024d5d664.mp4?t=1710631464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
